tv.amwa.maj.enumeration

Enum EmphasisType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EmphasisType>
      • tv.amwa.maj.enumeration.EmphasisType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EmphasisType>, MediaEnumerationValue

    public enum EmphasisType
extends Enum<EmphasisType>
implements MediaEnumerationValue

    Specifies the encoded audio signal pre-emphasis for sound data.

    The values associated with elements of this enumeration are specified in section 4 of EBU tech. 3250.

    See Also:
    AES3PCMDescriptor.getEmphasis(), TypeDefinitions.EmphasisType
